{"title":"Unit 6: Lesson 4, Exercise B","clock":true,"countdown":0,"attempts":0,"intro":{"buttons":{"start":"Start"},"content":[]},"activity":{"scenes":[{"block":"scene","name":"SC1","countdown":0,"instructions":{"open":true,"content":[{"block":"group","class":"flex gap-2 items-center","content":[{"block":"audio","class":"","file":"files/inst.mp3","wave":false,"autoplay":false,"id":"","name":"bWbx"},{"block":"text","class":"","text":"Read the passage and select the correct answer.","id":"","name":"gj70"}]}]},"content":[{"block":"group","class":"bg-slate-100 rounded p-3 my-2 max-w-3xl mx-auto","content":[{"marker":"","class":"flex justify-center m-5","content":[{"file":"files/img.jpg","class":"mask mask-circle w-3/4","id":"TCJZ","block":"image","name":"zZYZ"}],"background":"","id":"Axwr","block":"group","name":"SeF8"},{"marker":"","class":"m-5 p-5 grid bg-sky-200 rounded-xl shadow gap-4","content":[{"block":"text","class":"","text":"What do you normally do when looking for entertainment? <b>While</b> some people select a new <b>hobby</b> carefully, others just let a new hobby find them. Either way, when people want to be entertained and they are open to new ideas, they learn something, and therefore, they get <b>knowledge</b>.","name":"60Bg","hidden":false,"id":""},{"text":"For example, did you know that listening to or making <b>music</b> has been proven to have positive effects on our bodies? Doing one or the other increases blood flow to brain regions that generate and control emotions. So, practically, music improves our processes related to emotions.","class":"","id":"xLEi","block":"text","name":"eDNq"},{"text":"What about playing a <b>sport</b>? Playing a <b>sport</b> is another way of entertainment <b>as well as</b> a popular <b>hobby</b>. It turns out that playing a sport also has benefits for our brains. Creativity and memory are improved <b>as a consequence</b> of the effects exercise has on our bodies.  In general, practicing sports improves brain function.","class":"","id":"gz7uhGGw","block":"text","name":"OS8j"},{"text":"Nevertheless, watching <b>films</b> seems to be an activity that could be practiced merely for <b>fun</b>. On the other hand, when watching certain types of <b>films</b> and having an analytic process before, during and after watching them, different cognitive skills might be put into practice. In the end, <b>films</b> are considered a form of art and paying more attention to the arts is always a good option. Did you know Art may access many of the advanced processes of the human brain? Cognitively speaking, when focusing on the <b>arts</b>, the brain improves its plasticity.","class":"","id":"boLiaRkf","block":"text","name":"HXMY"}],"background":"","id":"M8Hb","block":"group","name":"lCCY"},{"marker":"","class":"grid gap-10 m-5","content":[{"marker":"","class":"text-xl","content":[{"text":"1)","class":"bg-yellow-400 p-1 mr-2 rounded","id":"A3jC","block":"text","name":"XCpd"},{"text":"This passage is about hobbies and entertainment.","class":"","id":"wNjZldln","block":"text","name":"ROci"},{"class":"mt-4","options":[{"text":"True","class":"","id":"27kD","block":"text","name":"3JWd"},{"text":"False","class":"","id":"o6sTuCuc","block":"text","name":"2oKt"}],"evaluation":"auto","showResult":false,"dropdown":false,"dropdownpos":"top","id":"UWsw","block":"option","name":"GDVw","attempts":0}],"background":"","id":"8Ru9","block":"group","name":"RDoo"},{"marker":"","class":"text-xl","content":[{"text":"2)","class":"bg-yellow-400 p-1 mr-2 rounded","id":"A3jCp9yQ","block":"text","name":"B3PG"},{"text":"Music is considered entertainment.","class":"","id":"wNjZldlnPzkn","block":"text","name":"2P9c"},{"class":"mt-4","options":[{"text":"True","class":"","id":"27kDGxsR","block":"text","name":"sD4D"},{"text":"False","class":"","id":"o6sTuCuc7y1Q","block":"text","name":"ZmNw"}],"evaluation":"auto","showResult":false,"dropdown":false,"dropdownpos":"top","id":"UWswPsfL","block":"option","name":"44Tn","attempts":0}],"background":"","id":"yTmBsN42","block":"group","name":"9UbC"},{"marker":"","class":"text-xl","content":[{"text":"3)","class":"bg-yellow-400 p-1 mr-2 rounded","id":"A3jCp9yQHvbP","block":"text","name":"FxyE"},{"text":"Practicing a sport only has positive physical effects.","class":"","id":"wNjZldlnPzknTvEb","block":"text","name":"wbdj"},{"class":"mt-4","options":[{"text":"False","class":"","id":"o6sTuCuc7y1Qzuj1","block":"text","name":"7cs2"},{"text":"True","class":"","id":"27kDGxsRLPS1","block":"text","name":"3A1A"}],"evaluation":"auto","showResult":false,"dropdown":false,"dropdownpos":"top","id":"UWswPsfLRkI0","block":"option","name":"xvXq","attempts":0}],"background":"","id":"uqpjlqNm","block":"group","name":"Xd0H"},{"marker":"","class":"text-xl","content":[{"text":"4)","class":"bg-yellow-400 p-1 mr-2 rounded","id":"A3jCp9yQHvbP4OHw","block":"text","name":"J887"},{"text":"Paying attention to the arts on a regular basis is beneficial for our brains.","class":"","id":"wNjZldlnPzknTvEbU36f","block":"text","name":"QR97"},{"class":"mt-4","options":[{"text":"True","class":"","id":"27kDGxsRLPS1zcOY","block":"text","name":"IWDr"},{"text":"False","class":"","id":"o6sTuCuc7y1Qzuj16aFi","block":"text","name":"gnJG"}],"evaluation":"auto","showResult":false,"dropdown":false,"dropdownpos":"top","id":"UWswPsfLRkI0tKCf","block":"option","name":"2JZ8","attempts":0}],"background":"","id":"GKJQxUYB","block":"group","name":"y5uI"},{"marker":"","class":"text-xl","content":[{"text":"5)","class":"bg-yellow-400 p-1 mr-2 rounded","id":"A3jCp9yQHvbP4OHwcP5U","block":"text","name":"3qmz"},{"text":"Having hobbies is just fun, not beneficial.","class":"","id":"wNjZldlnPzknTvEbU36fSFwY","block":"text","name":"E5BJ"},{"class":"mt-4","options":[{"text":"False","class":"","id":"o6sTuCuc7y1Qzuj16aFizCBv","block":"text","name":"48rz"},{"text":"True","class":"","id":"27kDGxsRLPS1zcOY65sh","block":"text","name":"y7LZ"}],"evaluation":"auto","showResult":false,"dropdown":false,"dropdownpos":"top","id":